snippet.title: Charlie, The Steak - iOS Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Charlie, The Steak is now available on the Apple App Store!
And the best of all - it is available for FREE!

Check this cool launch trailer to get the mood of the game and head to the App Store to download Charlie, The Steak now!

-------------------

Download now iPhone and iPod Touch:
http://bit.ly/charliethesteak

Download now for iPad:
http://bit.ly/charliethesteakhd

-------------------

http://www.dynamicdust.com
